ople\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"so many ways\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is so many to thank.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the first and most important to thank is Arty.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arty_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.9903202686245349, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arty_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arty_(musician)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Arty, you have no idea what you have done for me.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will spend the rest of our lives making sure you feel like the most-loved horse in the world and that you never ever want for anything.\\\"\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"the most-loved horse\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following Creswell's suicide, Ms Lyle went public to reveal the abuse she had suffered during their short relationship, describing her former partner as \\\"an incredibly violent and abusive individual\\\".\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Creswell's suicide\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Lyle\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"their short relationship\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram