t over again.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cycle\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every couple of weeks for those nine months, I did something that would be unacceptable to him.\\\"\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"those nine months\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another incident Ms Lyle described vividly was when Creswell threatened to throw her into a bath of bleach.\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creswell_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.987554077677569, \"rank\": 0.012602775486901014, \"text\": \"Creswell\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creswell_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creswell_railway_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another incident\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Lyle\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"a bath\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"bleach\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One evening I came home and I could smell it from downstairs; he had filled the bath with bleach,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"downstairs\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2903}, {\"ngram\": \"the bath\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2927}, {\"ngram\": \"bleach\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started screaming and someone actually came to the door.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know who that [person] was, but thank you.\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Someone came and banged on the door and he [Creswell] said: 'If you are quiet I will not put you in the bleach.'\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3111, \"end\": 3119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creswell_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.987554077677569, \"rank\": 0.012602775486901014, \"text\": \"Creswell\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creswell_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Creswell_railway_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Someone\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3074}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"the bleach\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I was quiet.\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I just got a 'normal' beating instead.\\\"\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 'normal' beating\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having escaped the abusive relationship, Ms Lyle has since competed all over the world in international dressage.\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the abusive relationship\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Lyle\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3288}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"international dressage\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group - calling itself the New Republican Movement - released a chilling video earlier this week.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The group\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": \"the New Republican Movement\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"a chilling video\", \"from\":